{"id":2243,"date":"2024-11-23T22:44:32","date_gmt":"2024-11-23T22:44:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=2243"},"modified":"2024-12-10T16:59:28","modified_gmt":"2024-12-10T16:59:28","slug":"move-relearner","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/move-relearner\/","title":{"rendered":"Move Relearner (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left widesecond\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Crater Town<\/strong> &#8211; Inside the house in the southeast corner of town<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Allows a selected Pok\u00e9mon to relearn any forgotten move <\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>Heart Scales<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td><strong>1 Move<\/strong> = 1 Heart Scale<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Start by flying to the Crater Town Pok\u00e9mon Center and go south.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/01-pokemon-unbound-walking-south-from-the-crater-town-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Walking south from the Crater Town Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking south from the Crater Town Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Enter the first house you see in the southeast corner of the town.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-house-at-the-edge-of-town.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the house at the edge of town. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the house at the edge of town.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Move Relearner is the only NPC inside the house.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/03-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-move-relearner.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the Move Relearner. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the Move Relearner.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Function<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/04-pokemon-unbound-being-asked-to-reteach-a-move.jpg\" alt=\"Being asked to reteach a move. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Being asked to reteach a move.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Move Relearner (also called the Move Reminder) allows any selected Pok\u00e9mon to relearn a forgotten move from its movepool in exchange for a Heart Scale.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"299\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Useful NPCs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":2244,"parent":2143,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[],"class_list":["post-2243","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/2243","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/ty